raw_mentions: The invention includes anti-RAGE antibodies that bind specifically to RAGE-expressing cells in vitro and in vivo, and antibodies that bind to human RAGE with a dissociation constant (Kd) in the range of from at least about 1×10<sup>−7 </sup>M to about 1×10<sup>−10 </sup>M.

The invention includes anti-RAGE antibodies that bind specifically to RAGE-expressing cells in vitro and in vivo, and antibodies that bind to human RAGE with a dissociation constant (Kd) in the range of from at least about 1×10<sup>−7 </sup>M to about 1×10<sup>−10 </sup>M.
